        "code": "SUCCESS",
        "msg": [
          {
            "type": "TEXT",
            "data": "Users:\n+-------+-------+\n|user_id|   city|\n+-------+-------+\n|     u1| Berlin|\n|     u2| Berlin|\n|     u3| Munich|\n|     u4|Hamburg|\n+-------+-------+\n\nOrders:\n+--------+-------+----------+---+-----+\n|order_id|user_id|product_id|qty|price|\n+--------+-------+----------+---+-----+\n|      o1|     u1|        p1|  2| 10.0|\n|      o2|     u1|        p2|  1| 30.0|\n|      o3|     u2|        p1|  1| 10.0|\n|      o4|     u2|        p3|  5|  7.0|\n|      o5|     u3|        p2|  3| 30.0|\n|      o6|     u3|        p3|  1|  7.0|\n|      o7|     u4|        p1| 10| 10.0|\n+--------+-------+----------+---+-----+\n\nProducts:\n+----------+------------+\n|product_id|product_name|\n+----------+------------+\n|        p1|   Ring VOLA|\n|        p2|  Ring POROG|\n|        p3|Ring TISHINA|\n+----------+------------+\n\n"
          }
        ]
      },
